{
  "stem": "25773.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they said-- and everything was prepared in Roman's place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was going to be a big feast, and so on-- saving food and fat, for months on end.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so we said, if we don't return to that place, the people-- they say that we are Jews, and in the, you know, [INAUDIBLE] of Jewish people, some of them were, the [? religious ?] or so on.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They will-- they will be marked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the best thing is to go back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they-- it was a sort of bravura, sort of brav-- because, you know, we knew it is a dangerous thing to come back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But yet, we decided to go, to risk it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was already not feeling very well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they let me sleep for few hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I must have had already fever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Where?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In room they had.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went shopping.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They brought a lot of goods.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- they must-- they must have been stuffed with money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were-- took a lot of provisions, and things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were very, very, very nicely received.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because it means for the-- for the Roman, and the villagers, that--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--we were there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came back, went shopping, and we didn't run away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You understand.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we decided that the feast will take place-- what do you know they have-- they had a family coming from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was decided there would be a vigilance, that now and again, one of the men would stay outside.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they will listen, in case somebody comes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- we had a little vodka, which was good, because you know, that I was--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--so tired and all of this-- exhausted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at certain point, we hear somebody says, cars are coming.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
